original_text:
figure
h = dendrogram( regularComponentLinkage, numCommodities, ...
    "Labels", commodityNames, ...
    "ColorThreshold", 0.8 );
ylabel( "Dissimilarity" )
title( "Commodity Price Series Clustering" )
subtitle( "Regular Component Correlation Distance" )
set( h, "LineWidth", 2 )
xtickangle( 45 )
grid( "on" )
box( "on" )
